Package com.salesforce.multicloudj.docstore.driver.codec

Interface Decoder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AliDecoder, AwsDecoder, FSDecoder, SpannerDecoder
    public interface Decoder
    Decoder defines methods for decoding a given format of data to the java native types such as User defined classes or the Map<String, Object>. It supports decoding null values, primitive types (booleans, strings, integers, floats), byte arrays, lists, and maps. Implementations of this interface are responsible for deserializing the data for a specific provider. The providers need to provide the decoder implementations for decoding to the provider/substrate specific format to the java native data types .
